      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation, ensuring a comfortable driving experience. The interior shows only minor signs of wear consistent with its age, and the exterior remains in great shape with no major blemishes. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for daily use or long-distance travel without needing immediate repairs.",
