    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between everyday utility and refined comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and well-preserved; the leather seats show light bolstering wear typical of careful use, and all electronic systems\u2014including the premium audio and dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight and true with no unusual noises or vibrations. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner's manual, and a folder of recent service receipts to verify its upkeep. This is a reliable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
